Query: Sort GDP by country and year

Write a query that returns GDP Growth for all coutries. Sort by countryName and year.

paragraphs.text:
%hive
select indicatorvalue as gdp_growth_value,
    year,
    countryname
from wdi_csv_parquet
where indicatorcode='NY.GDP.MKTP.KD.ZG'
    and indicatorvalue > 0
order by countryname, year
